{"application": "software-mentions", "version": "0.8.0", "date": "2024-10-07T11:55+0000", "md5": "A59679FE2600FF0E70B905D969928859", "mentions": [{"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "DISPUTool", "normalizedForm": "DISPUTool", "offsetStart": 0, "offsetEnd": 9}, "context": "DISPUTool is a tool designed to explore a dataset of presidential debates in the US for the period 1960-2016. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 5.7578086853027344e-05}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9288478493690491}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9997802376747131}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999326467514038}, "shared": {"value": true, "score": 0.9843372702598572}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "DISPUTool", "normalizedForm": "DISPUTool", "offsetStart": 0, "offsetEnd": 9}, "context": "DISPUTool relies on argumentation mining methods to automatically identify argumentative components (i.e., premises and claims) from the textual transcripts of political debates in English.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.00014770030975341797}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 5.3763389587402344e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9997802376747131}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999326467514038}, "shared": {"value": true, "score": 0.9843372702598572}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "DISPUTool", "normalizedForm": "DISPUTool", "offsetStart": 14, "offsetEnd": 23}, "context": "The corpus in DISPUTool is a collection of transcripts of the televised presidential candidate debates in United States from 1960 (Kennedy vs Nixon) until 2016 (Clinton vs Trump) covering 56 years of debates.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9196557998657227}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 7.152557373046875e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.3113021850585938e-06}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9997802376747131}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999326467514038}, "shared": {"value": true, "score": 0.9843372702598572}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "DISPUTool", "normalizedForm": "DISPUTool", "offsetStart": 16, "offsetEnd": 25}, "context": "More precisely, DISPUTool allows to explore and automatically identify argumentative components over the 39 political debates from the last 50 years of US presidential campaigns .", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 6.341934204101562e-05}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0004976987838745117}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9997802376747131}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999326467514038}, "shared": {"value": true, "score": 0.9843372702598572}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "DISPUTool", "normalizedForm": "DISPUTool", "offsetStart": 16, "offsetEnd": 25}, "context": "More precisely, DISPUTool provides the following facilities: Argumentative analysis of the US presidential debates:", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 8.7738037109375e-05}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 5.6624412536621094e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9997802376747131}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999326467514038}, "shared": {"value": true, "score": 0.9843372702598572}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "DISPUTool", "normalizedForm": "DISPUTool", "offsetStart": 16, "offsetEnd": 25}, "context": "A demo video of DISPUTool is available at https://github.com/ElecDeb60To16/DISPUTool.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.0007248520851135254}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.00018388032913208008}, "shared": {"value": true, "score": 0.9843372702598572}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9997802376747131}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999326467514038}, "shared": {"value": true, "score": 0.9843372702598572}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "DISPUTool", "normalizedForm": "DISPUTool", "offsetStart": 17, "offsetEnd": 26}, "context": "The main feature DISPUTool offers is to automatically analyze from the argumentative point of view such debates, i.e., the detection of argumentative components (premises and claims) in the textual transcripts of these political debates. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 5.030632019042969e-05}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.008394956588745117}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.5762786865234375e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9997802376747131}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999326467514038}, "shared": {"value": true, "score": 0.9843372702598572}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "DISPUTool", "normalizedForm": "DISPUTool", "offsetStart": 26, "offsetEnd": 35}, "context": "In this paper, we present DISPUTool, a tool designed to ease the work of historians and social science scholars in analyzing the argumentative content of political speeches. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 6.961822509765625e-05}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999326467514038}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 4.76837158203125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9997802376747131}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999326467514038}, "shared": {"value": true, "score": 0.9843372702598572}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "DISPUTool", "normalizedForm": "DISPUTool", "offsetStart": 26, "offsetEnd": 35}, "context": "Third, we will include in DISPUTool the possibility to highlight contradictions that can possibly hold between the viewpoints of the same candidate or candidates from the same political party on a particular topic discussed in the debates.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.001032710075378418}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.4670751690864563}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.6689300537109375e-06}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9997802376747131}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999326467514038}, "shared": {"value": true, "score": 0.9843372702598572}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "DISPUTool", "normalizedForm": "DISPUTool", "offsetStart": 28, "offsetEnd": 37}, "context": "In this paper, we presented DISPUTool, a tool to support humanities scholars in addressing an argumentative analysis of political debates. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 8.606910705566406e-05}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999313354492188}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.5762786865234375e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9997802376747131}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999326467514038}, "shared": {"value": true, "score": 0.9843372702598572}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "DISPUTool", "normalizedForm": "DISPUTool", "offsetStart": 75, "offsetEnd": 84}, "context": "A demo video of DISPUTool is available at https://github.com/ElecDeb60To16/DISPUTool.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.0007248520851135254}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.00018388032913208008}, "shared": {"value": true, "score": 0.9843372702598572}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9997802376747131}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999326467514038}, "shared": {"value": true, "score": 0.9843372702598572}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "DISPUTool", "normalizedForm": "DISPUTool", "offsetStart": 78, "offsetEnd": 87}, "context": "We have used the best performing model (LSTM with word-embedding features) in DISPUTool for the identification of argument components.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9997802376747131}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0007929205894470215}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9997802376747131}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999326467514038}, "shared": {"value": true, "score": 0.9843372702598572}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "DISPUTool", "normalizedForm": "DISPUTool", "offsetStart": 86, "offsetEnd": 95}, "context": "However, to the best of our knowledge, none of them take on the design of a tool like DISPUTool where the identification of premises and claims is addressed together with Named Entity Recognition (NER), supporting intelligent data exploration on political debate textual transcripts.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.00010335445404052734}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.647363543510437}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9997802376747131}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999326467514038}, "shared": {"value": true, "score": 0.9843372702598572}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "DISPUTool", "normalizedForm": "DISPUTool", "offsetStart": 197, "offsetEnd": 206}, "context": "First of all, we are annotating the US election corpus with relations between the argumentative components (i.e., support and attack), and we will train a classifier for this task as well, so that DISPUTool can be empowered with this further feature. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.004065275192260742}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.05637013912200928}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9997802376747131}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999326467514038}, "shared": {"value": true, "score": 0.9843372702598572}}}], "references": [], "runtime": 7512, "id": "3cbb44c0bfa0ed0c4ed2b219432faa4b9500f5e5", "metadata": {"id": "3cbb44c0bfa0ed0c4ed2b219432faa4b9500f5e5"}, "original_file_path": "../../datalake/Samuel/SOFTware-Sync/downloads/xml/hal-02381055.grobid.tei.xml", "file_name": "hal-02381055.grobid.tei.xml"}